&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/maedhroz/cassandra/237/workflows/641cd945-f194-4a4f-bc0b-5cbed0c2061f&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CircleCI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="17285204" author="adelapena" created="Tue, 16 Feb 2021 13:46:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The failure can also be reproduced by running the entire &lt;tt&gt;MigrationCoordinatorTest&lt;/tt&gt; suite, where 100 iterations in IDEA seem to be enough to see some failures. Confirmed that the patch fixes the problem, +1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17285369" author="adelapena" created="Tue, 16 Feb 2021 17:33:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to &lt;tt&gt;cassandra-3.0&lt;/tt&gt; as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/8d71e06c1c83df5ec29069e3be3352f1dcf1d1d2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;8d71e06c1c83df5ec29069e3be3352f1dcf1d1d2&lt;/a&gt; and merged up to &lt;tt&gt;trunk&lt;/tt&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The only merge conflict was just that in &lt;tt&gt;trunk&lt;/tt&gt; the modified &lt;tt&gt;MigrationCoordinatorTest&lt;/tt&gt; has been moved from the &lt;tt&gt;service&lt;/tt&gt; package to &lt;tt&gt;schema&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
